<section class="py-8" aria-label="Manifest">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 md-h2">manifest</h2>

  <p class="comment mb-6">What is metamodernism?</p>

  <div class="space-y-4 text-base" style="color: var(--text);">
    <p>
      <strong style="color: var(--syn-key);">Modernism</strong> believed in progress unconditionally.
      Build, scale, conquer. Naive faith in technology.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong style="color: var(--syn-key);">Postmodernism</strong> deconstructed everything.
      Nothing is real, nothing matters, everything is a construct.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong style="color: var(--syn-key);">Metamodernism</strong> oscillates between both.
      Sincere yet aware. Idealistic yet pragmatic.
      Building while knowing it might break.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p class="comment mt-8 mb-4">Applied to AI</p>

  <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
    <p class="md-li">Not <em>"AI will replace everyone"</em> <span class="comment" style="display:inline;">&mdash; hype</span></p>
    <p class="md-li">Not <em>"AI is a bubble"</em> <span class="comment" style="display:inline;">&mdash; cynicism</span></p>
    <p class="md-li"><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Human-AI symbiosis</strong>, where each amplifies the other</p>
  </div>
</section>
